Blaze Berdahl https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Blaze_Berdahl 0 Blaze Autumn Berdahl (born September 6, 1980) is an American actress, singer, rapper, voice-over actor, announcer, and narrator. She is perhaps best known for her roles as Lenni Frazier in the children's television series Ghostwriter and Ellie Creed in the film Pet Sematary (1989).
